    Auth -->|HMAC invite ticket + session audit| RuntimeSecrets
    Auth -->|Fabric CA register / enroll CSR| CA
    Auth -->|SecurityService ledger writes| ServiceRelay

    UploadAPI --> DISP
    DISP -->|sanitized AI text| AISvc
    AISvc --> SciBERT
    ProcessMgr --> UnifiedAgent
    ProcessMgr -. optional .-> AISvc
    UploadAPI -->|pin encrypted bytes| IPFSA
    UploadAPI -->|pin encrypted bytes| IPFSB
    UploadAPI -.->|best effort| RemotePin
    IPFSMon --> IPFSA
    IPFSMon --> IPFSB

    FabricProxy -->|run securedata-agent offline-*| OfflineCLI
    OfflineCLI --> Gateway
    ServiceRelay -->|Authorization: Bearer token| UnifiedAgent
    UnifiedAgent --> Gateway
    RiskEngine -->|BlockUserForSeconds| Gateway

    Gateway --> Chaincode
    Chaincode --> Ledger
    Chaincode -- chaincode events --> RiskEngine
    DownloadAPI -->|read CID via SecurityService| ServiceRelay
    DownloadAPI -->|cat encrypted blob| IPFSA
    DownloadAPI -->|fallback cat| IPFSB
```

