## Crypto Tool Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph Device["Browser trusted device boundary"]
        Passkey["WebAuthn passkey<br/>private key in authenticator"]
        DataPriv["Data encryption private key<br/>ECDH P-256, non-exportable working key"]
        FabricPriv["Fabric signing private key<br/>ECDSA P-256, non-exportable working key"]
        IDB["IndexedDB securedataLocalKeys<br/>protected local records"]
        Recovery["Recovery bundle<br/>Argon2id + AES-256-GCM"]
    end

    subgraph PublicState["Public / shared state"]
        WebAuthnPub["WebAuthn public key PEM<br/>stored in UserProfile"]
        DataPub["Data encryption public key<br/>SECUREDATA-ECDH-P256... on-ledger"]
        FabricCert["Fabric certificate<br/>from CSR enrollment"]
        AssetKeyMap["Asset.Keys map<br/>userID -> encrypted content key"]
        CID["IPFS CID of encrypted payload"]
    end

    subgraph ContentCrypto["Per-file content crypto"]
        Plain["Original file bytes"]
        FileHash["SHA-256 fileHash"]
        ContentKey["Random 32-byte content key"]
        ContentEnvelope["content envelope v2<br/>AES-256-GCM, 12-byte IV"]
        ContentAAD["AAD<br/>type, version, alg, assetId,<br/>fileHash, filename, metadataHash"]
        EncryptedBlob["Encrypted JSON envelope<br/>stored in IPFS"]
    end

    subgraph KeyEnvelope["Per-recipient key envelope v2"]
        RecipientPub["Recipient ECDH public key"]
        Ephemeral["Ephemeral ECDH P-256 keypair"]
        SharedSecret["ECDH shared secret"]
        HKDF["HKDF-SHA256<br/>salt 32 bytes, fixed info"]
        WrapKey["AES-256-GCM wrap key"]
        WrappedKey["SDC2:KEY:<base64 JSON><br/>encrypted content key"]
    end

    subgraph Signing["Fabric offline signing"]
        ProposalBytes["Proposal bytes from Go helper"]
        ProposalSig["DER ECDSA signature"]
        TxBytes["Prepared transaction bytes"]
        TxSig["DER ECDSA signature"]
        SignedSubmit["Signed proposal/transaction submitted"]
    end

    Passkey -->|challenge signatures| WebAuthnPub
    DataPriv --> IDB
    FabricPriv --> IDB
    DataPriv --> Recovery
    FabricPriv --> Recovery
    Recovery -. excludes .-> Passkey

    DataPriv -->|export public JWK only| DataPub
    FabricPriv -->|CSR public key| FabricCert

    Plain --> FileHash
    Plain --> ContentEnvelope
    ContentKey --> ContentEnvelope
    ContentAAD --> ContentEnvelope
    ContentEnvelope --> EncryptedBlob
    EncryptedBlob --> CID

    DataPub --> RecipientPub
    RecipientPub --> SharedSecret
    Ephemeral --> SharedSecret
    SharedSecret --> HKDF
    HKDF --> WrapKey
    ContentKey --> WrappedKey
    WrapKey --> WrappedKey
    WrappedKey --> AssetKeyMap

    ProposalBytes --> BrowserSign1["Browser signs locally"]
    FabricPriv --> BrowserSign1
    BrowserSign1 --> ProposalSig
    ProposalSig --> SignedSubmit
    TxBytes --> BrowserSign2["Browser signs locally"]
    FabricPriv --> BrowserSign2
    BrowserSign2 --> TxSig
    TxSig --> SignedSubmit

    Legacy["Legacy compatibility<br/>RSA-OAEP / AES-CBC"] -. readable migration path .-> ContentEnvelope
```

## Workflow Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start["Start local stack<br/>Fabric network, Kubo replicas, AI service,<br/>backend, Go agent, static UI"]
    Health["Health checks<br/>/health, /health/ipfs, agent /health, AI /health"]
    BootstrapNeeded{"SecurityService bootstrap needed?"}
    BootstrapTicket["POST /auth/bootstrap-ticket<br/>issue/reissue invite for SecurityService"]
    SecActivate["Activate SecurityService device<br/>passkey + local keys + Fabric CSR"]
    SecSession["SecurityService session"]
    CreateUsers["SecurityService creates users<br/>/auth/users -> Fabric CA register + ledger invite"]
    UserActivate["User activates device<br/>invite + passkey + local keys + CSR"]
    RecoveryGate{"Recovery bundle created?"}
    CreateRecovery["Create recovery bundle<br/>Argon2id + AES-GCM export<br/>MarkRecoveryBundleCreated"]
    Workspace["Role-aware workspace<br/>Dashboard, Assets, Audit, Security, Users, Settings"]

    Upload["Researcher uploads file"]
    Encrypt["Browser encrypts file<br/>AES-GCM content envelope + ECDH key envelope"]
    Sanitize["Backend validates + DISP sanitizes metadata"]
    StoreIPFS["Backend replicates encrypted blob to IPFS quorum"]
    Predict["AI predicts category from sanitized text"]
    CommitAsset["Browser signs CreateAsset<br/>chaincode forces Unverified"]
    SuggestDecision{"AI suggestion actionable?"}
    StoreSuggestion["MLService stores advisory suggestion<br/>only if actionable and above threshold"]
    NeedsReview["Manual category review required<br/>for every new asset"]
